text: Adetutu Akinmou Akikenju VI is the king (Oba) of the Yoruba State of Sabe in Benin. ==See also== *List of rulers of the Yoruba state of Sabe *List of current constituent African monarchs ==References== Category:21st-century Beninese people Category:Obas of Benin Category:Beninese Ahmadis Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
